{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"title":"set(clearFunc:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"clearFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GLib","externalID":"s:4GLib13ArrayProtocolPAAE3set9clearFuncyySvSgXCSg_tF","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol\/set(clearFunc:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/arrayprotocol\/set(clearfunc:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a function to clear an element of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"array"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"clearFunc","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify","text":"GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"clearFunc"},{"text":" will be called when an element in the array","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"data segment is removed and when the array is freed and data"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"segment is deallocated